title: Bravo State of the Housewives with Carlos King!
itunes:title: Bravo State of the Housewives with Carlos King!
description:
Housewives producer and host Carlos King stops by Everything Iconic to discuss the current state of the Bravo! Danny and Carlos discuss each Real Housewives franchise, who should return, best trips, and more! Carlos has a new pod called Reality with the King! (*Recorded May 2)
